{"tid":767170,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"一人5隻10年以上你最鍾意玩舊game","createTime":"2018-08-04T08:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T08:21:39.000Z","uid":191738,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"e418fb3c630ce28d467c719e032b2087cadcbb42","tid":767170,"uid":191738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:58:18.000Z","msg":"本貼以投票制進行，本人先舉5隻，你認同就係隻game後面加個icon 代表支持，你有其他建議就自己加一行。歡迎當中比d <del>掙扎</del>討論<br />\n<br />\n1. SimCity2000 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n近乎人拜第一隻game, 真係好好玩，會核爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我到依家都重係唔明點解抽水系統叫幫補<br />\n<br />\n2. 主題醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無玩過唔好話打過機，最記得有人狂嘔，第七八關要培訓醫生<br />\n<br />\n3. 地城守護者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反轉用惡魔打英雄，真係好震撼。隻最勁隻怪係冇差別攻擊<br />\n<br />\n4. 太閤立志傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知邊代，係dos玩，256色。好玩到仆街，重記得開game 無耐信長會叫你打個無可能打得入既城，結果重玩到打得入<br />\n<br />\n5. 大航海時代2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n世界觀，經濟觀都一流，學識左好多地理同特產"},{"pid":"2f2fb5c97761cdc03d4a2c2e528b0dd89180bcdc","tid":767170,"uid":39218,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"l4d"},{"pid":"c462bd47cecc4fc8dc765f78e0257033b7a273f3","tid":767170,"uid":54564,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T09:02:21.000Z","msg":"War3"},{"pid":"05fb8d09d3576b753fb58705cc0647731f243a9e","tid":767170,"uid":144064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T09:03:22.000Z","msg":"柏德之門"},{"pid":"4820747741ea17c65c82c9cfadc8fa794dcd10eb","tid":767170,"uid":122274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T09:04:28.000Z","msg":"超三"},{"pid":"a48976714121130c3e67fe9ae5ffcbb418a81bea","tid":767170,"uid":22624,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20